title: Are You Offended?
itunes:title: Are You Offended?
description:
What are you offended by? What pisses you off? What make you emotional? Have you ever taken a step back and asked "WHY does this offend me?" chances are it's because it was programmed into you. In this episode, I am going to talk about how to stop being offended and take back control of your own life.

Follow me on Instagram @RobDialJr https://www.instagram.com/robdialjr/
